<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Homepage</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
            <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">
                <svg class="bi me-2" width="40" height="32"><use xlink:href="#bootstrap"></use></svg>
                <span class="fs-4">Kitty Enterprises</span>
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/guestbook">Guestbook</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/newmessage">New message</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/ajaxmessage">Ajax message</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="px-4 py-5 my-5 text-center">
        <h1>Welcome to Kitty Enterprises</h1>
        <div class="container col-xl-10 col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5 bg-secondary">
            <h2 class="text-grey">What is Kitty Enterprises?</h2>
            <h4>The company is run by three cats Jatsi(CEO), Loki(COO), and their newest pawrtner Kida(CFO).</h4>
            <h4>Their main goal is that every cat in the world has a chance to live a nice and comfortable life.</h4>
            <div id="spacer" class="d-flex" style="height: 100px;">
                <div class="vr bg-secondary"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img src="/Application/betterloki.jpg" alt="jatsi" class="img-thumbnail">
                    <h2 class="fw-normal">Loki(COO)</h2>
                    <p>Some representative placeholder content for the three columns of text below the carousel. This is the first column.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img src="/Application/doublejatsi.jpg" alt="jatsi" class="img-thumbnail">
                    <h2 class="fw-normal">Jatsi(CEO)</h2>
                    <p>Another exciting bit of representative placeholder content. This time, we've moved on to the second column.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                  <img src="/Application/kida.jpg" alt="kida" class="img-thumbnail">
                    <h2 class="fw-normal">Kida(CFO)</h2>
                    <p>And lastly this, the third column of representative placeholder content.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
